# Fixture binaries must be stored byte-exact — the encrypted samples
# (.rpgmvp/.png_/.rpgmvo/.ogg_) round-trip through XOR decryption and any
# CRLF normalization would corrupt them. Mark all fixture asset types binary.
*.png   binary
*.ogg   binary
*.m4a   binary
*.rpgmvp binary
*.rpgmvo binary
*.png_  binary
*.ogg_  binary
